* {{cite web|title=Arabic Culture &amp; Traditions|url=http://www.pimsleurapproach.com/…/useful-li…/culture-guides/|access-date=18 December 2017|website=Pimsleur Approach}}{{Dead link|date=August 2020 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}
