=== Arab diaspora ===
{{main|Arab diaspora}}
[[File:The_Syrian_colony,_Washington_Street.jpg|thumb|[[Syrian Americans|Syrian immigrants]] in [[New York City]], as depicted in 1895]]
[[File:Arab people around the world.svg|thumb|Countries with significant Arab population and descendants.

